Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
What to watch on Netflix, Hulu & Prime Video. Find out what's coming out soon and what you should be watching right now. Discover new movies & TV shows to binge. I'll tell you what's streaming and why you should be watching it. From action packed to thrillers, magic and murder mysteries, reality TV and more listen up to find them. You'll never be bored again!

Follow @WhatsStreaming on Instagram
